OL,3,CMan, 24, with terminal brain tumour
OL,4,Cjoins calls for more research
OL,6,FA 24-year-old man from Farnham who has
OL,7,Fbeen given less than two years to live
OL,8,Fis joining calls for more research
OL,9,Finto brain tumours.
OL,11,FMax Vardy underwent tests last summer
OL,12,Fafter getting persistent headaches and
OL,13,Fnumbness in his leg.
OL,15,FHe was diagnosed with a grade four
OL,16,Fglioma - a highly aggressive tumour
OL,17,Fand a terminal condition.
