OL,3,CMan, 24, with terminal brain tumour
OL,4,Cjoins calls for more research
OL,6,FAround 3,200 people are diagnosed each
OL,7,Fyear with a glioblastoma with 25% of
OL,8,Fpeople with this type of brain tumour
OL,9,Fliving longer than a year.
OL,11,FHistorically 1% percent of spending on
OL,12,Fcancer research goes to research into
OL,13,Fbrain tumours.
OL,15,FMax is joining calls alongside the
OL,16,Fcharity Brain Tumour Research for more
OL,17,Finvestment into finding a cure.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
