OL,3,CMan, 24, with terminal brain tumour
OL,4,Cjoins calls for more research
OL,6,FKaren Noble, Director of Research,
OL,7,FBrain Tumour Research, said: "There
OL,8,Fhaven't been any changes with the
OL,9,Ftreatment protocol in decades.
OL,11,F"It will be surgery for those patients
OL,12,Fthat can have an operation and that
OL,13,Fwill really depend on their overall
OL,14,Fhealth and also where the tumour is
OL,15,Flocated in the brain - followed by
OL,16,Fradiotherapy and chemotherapy.
OL,18,F"But we know that, where the tumour
OL,19,Fhas been removed, it will come back,
OL,20,Fit will recur - and then the treatment
OL,21,Foptions are even more limited."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
