OL,3,CMan, 24, with terminal brain tumour
OL,4,Cjoins calls for more research
OL,6,FDespite his diagnosis, Max says he's
OL,7,Fdetermined to cherish every moment,
OL,8,Fproposing to his girlfriend Georgie
OL,9,Flast September.
OL,11,FHe said she's been "amazing", adding:
OL,12,F"Since getting diagnosed, every night
OL,13,Fthat I've been in hospital she's slept
OL,14,Fon a chair next to me and just
OL,15,Fsupported me unbelievable amounts
OL,16,Femotionally but also in just living
OL,17,Flife and giving me hope and something
OL,18,Fto fight for."
